title: Tutenstein Season 03
description:
Tutenstein Season 03

12-year-old Cleo's knowledge of Ancient Egypt is turned on its head when a bolt of lightning awakens the mummified body of child Pharaoh Tut-ankh-en-set-amun on display in a local museum. Together with her pet cat Luxor, she attempts to help him adjust to life in the 21st Century.

Thanks goes to all the individual rippers of this series.
